### Create lead
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ana",
  "lastName": "Lopez",
  "email": "ana.lopez@example.com",
  "phone": "+34-600-000-001",
  "companyName": "Acme Corp",
  "source": "Website",
  "notes": "Interested in enterprise plan"
}

### List leads
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/leads?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc

### Get lead by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/leads/1

### Convert lead
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/leads/1/convert

### List contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc

### List companies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/companies?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
